1.
查看mysql-server版本 yum info mysql-server(centos6默认安装为5.1版本)
chkconfig --list mysqld(查看是否开机启动)
chkconfig mysqld on(设为开机启动)
ss -ntl;service mysqld start(启动3306端口服务)
2.
mysql创建密码提示“Error: Password hash should be a 41-digit hexadecimal number“
解决办法：https://blog.csdn.net/qq575217319/article/details/41441263
3.
mysql命令后提示“Can 't connect to local MySQL server through socket '/tmp/mysql.sock '(2) "
解决办法：https://blog.csdn.net/hjf161105/article/details/78850658
